      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.On2ZrPJTe8FURsXY]{Operative Exploit}</p>\n<p>You&rsquo;re adept at piloting terrestrial vehicles. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to skill checks to use tricks during a vehicle chase. Once per vehicle chase while you&rsquo;re piloting a vehicle, you can perform the double maneuver action, taking a &ndash;2 penalty to each skill check rather than a &ndash;4 penalty (or no penalty if your vehicle&rsquo;s full speed is at least 50 feet faster than the fastest enemy vehicle&rsquo;s full speed). You must have the @Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.NaGCVIyrwQsH8bV5]{Uncanny Pilot (Ex)} exploit to learn this exploit.</p>"
